reviews.text:
Excellent, delicious coffee. If you bring your own cup you get a discount! Wish it was closer to my workplace.

It also has a buy 1 get 1 free Monday 😃. Great service from the staff too.
Nice atmosphere to sit for a good coffee. No line on a Sunday, which is almost unheard of in central HK...
Great coffee & homemade chicken wrap. 😋😋😋

Tasty coffee for a standard HK price.
